title: A Vegan Critique of "Animal Rights: The Abolitionist Approach", by Gary Francione.
description: Here's the link to an earlier video (mentioned in this one) directly replying to Gary Francione (using clips of one of his public lectures) on the issue of slavery, as he interprets in his theory of vegan activism: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hVk-mr9hRVs
